title: Jenks Criterium
description: Jenks Criterium and Masters State Criterium Championships
course: Figure 8 course with 6 left turns and 2 right turns.  Very flat, very fast, and with brand new asphalt on majority of course.
registration: Register on-line through June 24th at usacycling.org or go to the link at jenkscriterium.com.  Registration fee is $35 ($20 for juniors).  $5 Late fee in effect starting on June 23rd.  On-site registration will close 15 minutes prior to each race.
notes: Event will be rain or shine.  Wheel pit will be \"wheels in/wheels out\".  Free lap rule in effect until lap counter begins.
directions:
Start/Finish line will be located at 2nd & Main in downtown Jenks, OK.
Please park in desitnated areas (see map at jenkscriterium.com)

title: Tour de Trykes Criterium
flyer_url: Tour de Trykes Criterium Flyer, 2011, V02.pdf updated 630.pdf
description: Tour de Trykes Criterium, downtown historic Enid Oklahoma
course: Downtown Enid Oklahoma, 8 corners, slight uphill finish. Free lap rule will apply except for last three laps of race. Wheels in and wheels out for pit. There will be at least one pit on the course.
registration: online registration ends 8/31/2011, late registration fee is 3.00,in addition to entry fee. day of registration fee is 5.00 plus entry fee. All participants are encouraged to register online-----
directions: I-35 South/North exit Hwy 412 West to Enid 28 miles turn north on Independence Street to race course.
